---
// Features Component
---

<section class="features-section" id="funcionalidades">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <div class="section-badge">Como funciona</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">
        A IA faz o trabalho pesado. <span class="gradient-text">Seu time fecha a venda.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="section-desc">
        Não é mais um CRM pra preencher. É uma máquina de vendas que qualifica, organiza e entrega o lead pronto pro seu vendedor.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature 1 -->
    <div class="feature-row reveal">
      <div class="feature-content">
        <h3 class="feature-title">Lead respondido em segundos, não em horas</h3>
        <p class="feature-text">
          A IA lê a mensagem, entende o que o cliente precisa e responde como seu melhor vendedor — 24 horas por dia. Cliente quente? Prioriza. Curioso? Qualifica. Sem potencial? Não desperdiça o tempo do seu time.
        </p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#8257e5" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
            Entende a intenção real do cliente
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#8257e5" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
            Coleta dados da conversa automaticamente
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://app.kronoshub.com.br/login" class="feature-cta" id="cta-comecar-ia-1">
          COMEÇAR AGORA
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-visual">
        <div class="visual-mockup">
          <div class="chat-bubble left">Qual plano atende nossa agência de 15 pessoas?</div>
          <div class="chat-bubble right">
            Perfeito! Para 15 usuários o Scale é ideal.
            <div class="ai-tag">Respondido pela AI</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature 2 -->
    <div class="feature-row reverse reveal">
      <div class="feature-content">
        <h3 class="feature-title">Do chat ao funil de vendas, sem digitar nada</h3>
        <p class="feature-text">
          Cada conversa vira negócio no CRM automaticamente. O vendedor abre o painel e já sabe o que o cliente precisa, o que foi conversado e qual o próximo passo. Zero retrabalho.
        </p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#8257e5" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
            Negócios criados automaticamente no funil de vendas
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#8257e5" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
            </svg>
            Resumo completo da conversa feito pela IA
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://app.kronoshub.com.br/login" class="feature-cta" id="cta-comecar-ia-2">
          COMEÇAR AGORA
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-visual">
         <div class="visual-mockup crm-mockup">
            <div class="pipe-col">
               <div class="pipe-title">Lead Novo</div>
               <div class="pipe-card deal"></div>
               <div class="pipe-card deal"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="pipe-col">
               <div class="pipe-title">Qualificado</div>
               <div class="pipe-card deal active">
                  <div class="pulse"></div>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature 3 (desativado) -->
    <!--
    <div class="feature-row reveal">
      <div class="feature-content">
        <h3 class="feature-title">Gestão Onipresente</h3>
        <p class="feature-text">
          WhatsApp, Direct do Instagram, Messenger e Site reunidos para seu time não precisar mais saltar de app em app. Uma interface, controle total.
        </p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Dashboard de Caixa de Entrada unificada</li>
          <li>Tempo de Primeira Resposta monitorado</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://app.kronoshub.com.br/login" class="feature-cta" id="cta-comecar-ia-3">COMECE AGORA</a>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-visual"></div>
    </div>
    -->
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features-section {
    padding: 80px 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .section-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--dark-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--dark-3);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 36px);
    font-weight: 500;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .section-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .feature-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 80px;
    margin-bottom: 120px;
  }

  .feature-row.reverse {
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
  }

  .feature-row:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .feature-content {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .feature-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 28px);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .feature-text {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
  }

  .feature-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .feature-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid #8257e5;
    background: transparent;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .feature-cta:hover {
    background: #8257e5;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .feature-cta-gray {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 44px;
    padding: 0 28px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--dark-3);
    background: transparent;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .feature-cta-gray:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-subtle);
  }

  .feature-cta-filled {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 44px;
    padding: 0 28px;
    color: #ffffff;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: none;
    background: #8257e5;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .feature-cta-filled:hover {
    background: #996dff;
  }

  .feature-visual {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .visual-mockup {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 440px;
    background: var(--dark-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--dark-3);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    box-shadow: 0 30px 60px var(--shadow-color);
  }

  .chat-bubble {
    padding: 16px 20px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 80%;
  }

  .chat-bubble.left {
    background: var(--dark-3);
    border: 1px solid var(--dark-3);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-right: auto;
    border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;
  }

  .chat-bubble.right {
    background: rgba(130, 87, 229, 0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(130, 87, 229, 0.3);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-left: auto;
    border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-tag {
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #8257e5;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .crm-mockup { display: flex; gap: 16px; }
  .pipe-col { flex: 1; }
  .pipe-title { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .pipe-card { height: 48px; background: var(--dark-3); border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .pipe-card.active { border: 1px solid #8257e5; background: rgba(130, 87, 229, 0.15); display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 0 12px; }
  .pulse { width: 8px; height: 8px; background: #8257e5; border-radius: 50%; box-shadow: 0 0 12px #8257e5; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .feature-row, .feature-row.reverse {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 48px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .feature-row {
      margin-bottom: 64px;
    }
    .section-header {
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }
  }
</style>
